Project Setup:

- Initialize a new React project.
- Install necessary packages: react-router-dom, firebase, redux, react-redux, @reduxjs/toolkit, and any other needed libraries.
- Configure Firebase in the project.
- Set up Firebase Authentication, Firestore, and Storage.
- Set up Redux for state management.

Authentication Module: 

- Implement user registration and login using Firebase Authentication.
- Protect routes based on authentication status (e.g., Admin Panel, User Profile).

UI/UX Design:

- Create wireframes using Figma for both the client and admin interfaces.
- Design reusable components: Header, Footer, Buttons, Forms, Cards.
- Ensure responsive design for all devices.

Accommodation Listings Module:

- Create a AccommodationList component to display accommodations.
- Implement components for displaying hotel details: Gallery, Map, Price, Facilities, and Policies.
- Add functionality for users to save accommodations to favorites and share details.

Booking Functionality:

- Develop a booking form with fields for check-in, check-out, number of rooms, and guests.
- Implement a payment gateway for booking payments.
- Store booking details in Firestore.

User Profile Module:

- Create a UserProfile component for viewing and editing profile information.
- Display user bookings and favorite accommodations.
- Implement functionality for users to update their profile.

Admin Panel Module:

- Develop an AdminPanel component for managing accommodations and reservations.
- Implement CRUD operations for accommodations (add, edit, delete).
- Implement CRUD operations for reservations (approve, modify, cancel).

Search Functionality:

- Implement a search bar to filter accommodations based on location, price, and other filters.
- Ensure that search results update the URL to maintain state.

Reviews & Ratings Module:

- Create a Reviews component where users can leave reviews and ratings for accommodations.
- Store and display reviews in Firestore.

Notifications Module:

- Implement a notification system for booking confirmations and updates.
- Send notifications via Firebase and display them in the app.

Security & Compliance:

- Implement security measures to protect user data and transactions.
- Ensure compliance with relevant regulations for data protection.